data.enText: a sport in which two people fight by holding each other and trying to throw or force the other one to the ground

tr: the sport of hand-to-hand struggle between unarmed contestants who try to throw each other down
the act of engaging in close hand-to-hand combat
example: we watched his grappling and wrestling with the bully

value.def: Wrestling is a sport in which two people wrestle and try to throw each other to the ground.
